### Feature 5: Nearby Place Search URL Construction

**As a developer**, I want to construct nearby place search URLs, so I can search around a coordinate using radius or distance ranking with validation for incompatible options.

**Expected Behavior / Usage:**

The input is a JSON command with `endpoint` set to `places_nearby`, an API key, a coordinate `location`, and either radius-based or rank-by-distance options. Optional filters include `type`, `keyword`, `language`, `minprice`, `maxprice`, `name`, and page token. The output is one `url=<full URL>` line for valid combinations. If distance ranking is requested without at least one textual filter, or if radius and ranking are combined, the output is a normalized `error=invalid_request` block with a rule identifier.

**Test Cases:** `rcb_tests/public_test_cases/feature5_places_nearby_urls.json`

```json
{
    "description": "Build a nearby place search URL from a coordinate, either radius-based or distance-ranked, including search filters and normalized validation errors for invalid ranking combinations.",
    "cases": [
        {
            "input": {
                "api_key": "MY_API_KEY",
                "endpoint": "places_nearby",
                "location": {
                    "lat": -33.8670522,
                    "lng": 151.1957362
                },
                "radius": 500
            },
            "expected_output": "url=https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/nearbysearch/json?location=-33.8670522,151.1957362&radius=500&key=MY_API_KEY\n"
        },
        {
            "input": {
                "api_key": "MY_API_KEY",
                "endpoint": "places_nearby",
                "location": {
                    "lat": -33.8670522,
                    "lng": 151.1957362
                },
                "radius": 500,
                "type": "restaurant",
                "keyword": "cruise"
            },
            "expected_output": "url=https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/nearbysearch/json?location=-33.8670522,151.1957362&radius=500&type=restaurant&keyword=cruise&key=MY_API_KEY\n"
        }
    ]
}
```

