    "description": "Build request URLs for time zone lookup and browser/mobile geolocation lookup, preserving the distinct service host and query parameters required by each endpoint.",
    "cases": [
        {
            "input": {
                "api_key": "MY_API_KEY",
                "endpoint": "timezone",
                "location": {
                    "lat": 38.908133,
                    "lng": -77.047119
                },
                "timestamp": 1458000,
                "language": "en"
            },
            "expected_output": "url=https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/timezone/json?location=38.908133,-77.047119&timestamp=1458000&language=en&key=MY_API_KEY\n"
        },
        {
            "input": {
                "api_key": "MY_API_KEY",
                "endpoint": "geolocation"
            },
            "expected_output": "url=https://www.googleapis.com/geolocation/v1/geolocate?key=MY_API_KEY\n"
        }
    ]
}
```

